desc: Nawlins Praline Candy is a candy store that sells a variety of items, such as our Famous New Orleans Pecan Pralines, Coconut Pralines, Chocolate Pralines, Praline Brownies, Chocolate Turtles, Brownies, Marshmallow Rocky Road, Almond Bark, Pecan Bark, Chocolate Covered Pretzels and More.
